    <bug_when>2014-10-24 23:45:54 -0400</bug_when>
    <thetext>Presently we operate in loose vs varargs modes only.

Change should be simple. Start in strict mode and let the engine slip
into loose mode if required and adjust the inference kind. 

There are only a couple of places that need this change, searching for
isPrimitiveType in CTF.java should catch them.

Note: we should go only from strict to loose. Never from varargs to loose.</thetext>
